data.description: Beautiful, 2013 home in desirable Sawgrass at Suntree! The covered entry & charming porch provide a warm welcome to this lovingly maintained home with fresh interior paint (2023). Gourmet kitchen features double oven, gas cooktop, 42-inch cabinets, & granite countertops, plus a convenient island, butler's pantry, & customized walk-in pantry. Generously-sized owner's suite offers tranquil views, cozy sitting/office area, & customized walk-in closet. Master bath has double vanities, garden tub, & walk-in shower. Second floor has a bonus room, 2 more BD & full baths. First-floor suite with walk-in closet & private bath can serve as guest room or in-law suite. Additional highlights include tile & hand-scraped hardwood floors, coffered dining room ceiling, plantation shutters, tankless gas water heater & other energy efficient ''Green Home'' features, brick paver drive, ''porte cochere,'' & oversized two-car garage with tons of storage. Spacious outdoor area rounds out the home. The trussed lanai is 10'x40' with a large backyard. Why wait to build when this Holiday Builders Hemingway model is move-in ready & shows like new? You'll be nestled in an established gated neighborhood in the heart of Suntree/Viera, convenient to shopping, dining, & top-rated schools, just a 15-minute drive to the beach & less than 1 hour to OIA & Orlando.
